      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thought about it a bit better: In addition to the uid/gid change for the intermediate directories, can they also have 0755 mode? The eventual mountpoint can still have 0700? Otherwise this can break some of the potential users: https://chrome-internal-review.googlesource.com/c/chromeos/cheets-scripts/+/572734 (since no user except root would be able to traverse to that directory).",
